Kris Jenner has opened up about filming The Kardashians amidst Kim Kardashian's split from Kanye West. During an Australia's The Daily Telegraph published on Saturday the Kardashian matriarch revealed how she handled her daughter's divorce from the rapper. "It's very fresh and new to us, too," she said, before explaining how the breakup will affect the family's new reality TV series. "We haven't been filming all that long. As with all the relationships in my family, we try to be as transparent as we can.".